cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.DS 

This paper deals with optimizing search queries for Twitter data, which involves information retrieval (IR) techniques. Therefore, cs.IR is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves machine learning techniques for topic classification (cs.SI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper deals with large datasets (cs.SD) and optimization algorithms (cs.DS).
